channel.title: People on server, but can't post status?
channel.description: I was able to post my server status on moparscape but not on codefasga? Any ideas? my server is running, people are playing on it, and im 100% sure its not already on the codefasga list. I've checked it multiple times. I attempt to post my server status and it says an unknown error has occurred. Please help.
